                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Valenti H<lb break="no" n="2"/>ostiliano <lb n="3"/>Messio Q<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>i</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="4"/>nto nobili<lb break="no" n="5"/>ssimo <expan><abbr>Cae</abbr><ex>sari</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivitas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Trib</abbr><ex>ocorum</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>a <expan><abbr>Vro</abbr><ex>comago</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>eugas</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende Fragmente einer Leugensäule, ursprünglich vier Fragmente noch erhalten, Lesung nach CIL 13, 09097, wo noch alle vier Fragmente wiedergegeben sind. Funddatum: zwischen 1850 und 1858.</p>
            </div>
